      <scopecontent id="aspace_scope">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection spans the years 1901-2004, while the bulk of the material is from 1914-1956. It consists mainly of announcements for debates and newspaper clippings regarding the results of the competitions. In addition, the collection contains photographs of the Debate Society throughout its history and notes regarding its founding in 1914.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
